WildfireForms & Forms Controllers

Expected use of forms as partials:

<?=partial("forms/X", array('cms_content'=>$cms_content))?>

X is either an extension in your overwritten form controller or one of the built ins:

_callback
_contact
_subscribe


WildfireFormNotify

Handle emails for the above. DOES NOT provide views for the emails.

Admin Controllers

CMS modules provided for each of built in forms